node.person.name: Dave Kashen
node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
We're excited about companies that are leveraging fundamental changes in the world to create meaningful companies that improve people's lives. We want to back the most significant companies of tomorrow, and help them operate as conscious, win-for-all businesses.

Some of the fundamental changes we're intrigued by include:
- AI
- Robotics & automation
- AR/VR
- Genetics & preventive health
- Blockchain
- BrainTech & mental health
- Sustainability / renewable energy

Ross Blankenship helps startups that want to grow and scale into the America's next top startups.

node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
We are building a recession-resilient portfolio by investing in founders leveraging deep tech (AI, Robotics, etc.) to solve global market problems around scarcity and inefficiency - everything from farming to financial audits.

Those startups that bring a diverse perspective (age, ethnicity, gender, geography, etc.) and have an intimate knowledge of the pain points they are tackling are those startups that will succeed and provide outsized returns to investors and society.
